      <alternative lang="sī. syā. kaṃ. ka.">sammāsamādhi</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <previous> Sāvatthinidānaṃ. Ariyaṃ vo, bhikkhave, sammāsamādhiṃ desessāmi saupanisaṃ saparikkhāraṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamo ca, bhikkhave, ariyo sammāsamādhi saupaniso saparikkhāro? Seyyathidaṃ – sammādiṭṭhi…pe… sammāsati </previous>
  </note>
